title: Features & Benefits of a K&N Air Intake System on 2011-2013 Mazda 3, 2.0L
description: Get the run down on just what you can expect from installing a K&N Air Intake (part # K&N 69-6031TS) on your 2011-2013 Mazda 3, 2.0L.

asset.title: K&N Air Intake System Overview for 2011, 2012 & 2013 Mazda 3, 2.0L
asset.description:
This video is an overview of the K&N 69-6031TS air intake system with a 2.0 liter engine. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-6031TS

This intake system created an estimated gain of 5.6 horsepower at 5,743 RPM and 4.3 lb. ft. of torque at 3,364 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. See how easy it is to add more performance to your car with this air intake system.
